VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT android:inputType.*(?:textPassword|textVisiblePassword|numberPassword)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:android:importantForAutofill\s*=\s*"(?:no|noExcludeDescendants)"
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects password input fields that do not disable the Android autofill framework.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Autofill Not Disabled on Sensitive Input Fields.
